o long and with absolute seriousness. \u003cbr /\u003eAnd when they are past this discussion, they decide to order equipment for their club, this is the letter they send to the supplier:\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eDear Sir,\u003cbr /\u003ePlease send to our team two junior willard bats, six balls, wickets and other things quick. It is very urgent. We shall send you money afterwards. Dont fear. Please be urgent. \u003cbr /\u003eRegards\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIn their world, it seems only they exist. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eThe central character Swami is quite a selfish chap and I was nodding my head a couple times wishing I could give him a lesson or two. He gets into trouble most times because of this - but then I'm thinking most boys 6 or 7 years old cant be expected to think much beyond themselves. :)","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1384536?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"indian-authors","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1384536?shelf=indian-authors"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/655718945"},"likeCount":11,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":1,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:2580971":{"id":2580971,"__typename":"User","legacyId":2580971,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1525349534i/2580971._UY200_CR33,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":774,"viewableName":"Smiley ","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/2580971-smiley","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":18},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.7CbTYaMtZoG-FA3Dh-0SZg":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.7CbTYaMtZoG-FA3Dh-0SZg","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.bo